commentary: NM Odhiambo to Mohammad Nabi, SIX runs dropped, hit hard down the ground in the air. Looks like it's going all the way but the fielder Shem Ngoche gets round to it before juggling the ball not once, but three times before the ball drops over the rope. Big chance for Kenya to take control
